message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you this product. I think it could be very valuable for you. I'm asking for $14,000.
Hello Alice, thank you for the offer. I appreciate the value of the product, but I can only pay up to $12,000 for it.
Hello Bob, I understand your position, but the product is worth a lot to me. How about we meet in the middle at $13,000?
Hello Alice, I appreciate your willingness to negotiate. I would like to propose a price of $12,500 for the product.
